&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    これは、&lt;a href=&quot;https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%B1%E6%9C%AC%E9%A1%98%E5%AF%BA&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;東本願寺&lt;/a&gt;のもう一つの大きなお寺の門です。この写真では、木と金の作品がはっきりと見えます。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">Another large temple gate, this one at Higashi Honganji, showing the detailed wood and gold work.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2101_IMG_2163.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Seiryo-ji・清涼寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210115/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Seiryo-ji・清涼寺" /><published>2021-01-15T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-01-15T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/seiryo-ji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210115/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
